{
  "stem": "22004.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was going with a half a million to Lodz by bringing [NON-ENGLISH] for the city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Katowice, it was a very big city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was going with millions, with half a millions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When she find out, she dropped everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She came to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Money.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Half a million money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Twice to Lodz buy an [NON-ENGLISH] for Katowice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- in zlotys.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, Polish money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So anyway, she came to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She dropped it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then I said, well, you have to go back with your partner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You to get some money, you have to get married.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She's got before husband and a child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They destroyed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So anyway, she went back, but she didn't go-- she went to him, and he said-- she went to him, she saw him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he didn't ask her for-- on the brothers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She got mad and she left there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then she came back to Waldenburg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, what did you do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have to get some money from him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were his partner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So anyway, she asked me I got a girl, or if I got married or what.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can't find nobody after the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She said, I got a girl for you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So after which she gave me a letter to see my wife.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my wife got with her sister a supermarket in Katowice, in the same city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So anyway, I took money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I got a-- my sister told me it's a lot of letter there in Katowice.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I started to get some money from my friends for my work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I got about six shoemakers already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I got a shop.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I take all the money what I can get it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I went there, and I saw my wife.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
